GeneralData.Title: O salutaris hostia
GeneralData.Notes: Notes corrected once Original text added 10-9-2007 Editorial accidentals added 29-9-2007 Modern texting. This is setting was obviously composed for a 7-verse hymn strophe. Original texting pays no attention to verse structure. For the editorial text verses from O salutaris have been repeated (majority vote for ambiguous cases) changed maximae to longae; normalised final bar; removed signature indication from accidental flats in source Revised by Ted, 26-12-2007 Altered F-clefs; ae -> e 28-12-2007 Ted: added version info 9/2008
